outside will fall into place.

00:10:10.150 --> 00:10:13.150 align:middle line:84%
I am sensible and in
control of my finances.

00:10:13.150 --> 00:10:16.570 align:middle line:84%
I'm creating total
financial success

00:10:16.570 --> 00:10:20.500 align:middle line:84%
in an easy and relaxed manner,
a healthy and positive mood,

00:10:20.500 --> 00:10:25.310 align:middle line:84%
in its own perfect time for
the highest good of all.

00:10:25.310 --> 00:10:27.270 align:middle line:84%
>> When you get back
to the realization,

00:10:27.270 --> 00:10:29.660 align:middle line:84%
the understanding of the one
thing that you have control

00:10:29.660 --> 00:10:33.260 align:middle line:84%
