point it's like, OK,

00:10:46.280 --> 00:10:47.450 align:middle line:90%
I think it's possible.

00:10:47.450 --> 00:10:49.130 align:middle line:84%
It's like, I think
it is possible.

00:10:49.130 --> 00:10:50.240 align:middle line:90%
You get to like, hope.

00:10:50.240 --> 00:10:51.720 align:middle line:84%
This is the positive
thinking part of you.

00:10:51.720 --> 00:10:53.095 align:middle line:84%
It's like, I hope
this works out.

00:10:53.095 --> 00:10:54.748 align:middle line:84%
And then you get this
