00:10:56.540 --> 00:10:58.490 align:middle line:84%
And then you finally
get to this place of

00:10:58.490 --> 00:11:04.760 align:middle line:84%
like, I don't care what or how,
but this is going to happen.

00:11:04.760 --> 00:11:06.450 align:middle line:90%
This thing is done.

00:11:06.450 --> 00:11:07.250 align:middle line:90%
It's complete.

00:11:07.250 --> 00:11:08.660 align:middle line:90%
It's complete in my mind.

00:11:08.660 --> 00:11:10.340 align:middle line:90%
It's complete in my body.

00:11:10.340 --> 00:11:11.670 align:middle line:90%
It's complete in my soul.

00:11:11.670 --> 00:11:14.770 align:middle line:84%
I am there before I
actually get the thing.

00:11:14.770 --> 00:11:17.930 align:middle line:84%
And you need to
hold that alignment

00:11:17.930 --> 00:11:20.830 align:middle line:84%
and give the world
and people and things,

00:11:20.830 --> 00:11:26.290 align:middle line:84%
circumstances, an opportunity
to work out for you.

00:11:26.290 --> 00:11:29.320 align:middle line:84%
>> It's all about creating
something out of apparently

00:11:29.320 --> 00:11:31.040 align:middle line:90%
nothing.

00:11:31.040 --> 00:11:34.100 align:middle line:84%
To me, I look at it as a
completely magical process,

00:11:34.100 --> 00:11:35.160 align:middle line:90%
in a way.

00:11:35.160 --> 00:11:37.620 align:middle line:84%
You don't have to use
those words at all.

00:11:37.620 --> 00:11:42.080 align:middle line:84%
You can just say strategic
planning has its results,

00:11:42.080 --> 00:11:44.490 align:middle line:90%
whatever words you want to use.

00:11:44.490 --> 00:11:46.550 align:middle line:84%
But for me, what
it does get down to

00:11:46.550 --> 00:11:51.440 align:middle line:84%
is the basic, deep mystery
of all of creation.

00:11:51.440 --> 00:11:56.130 align:middle line:84%
We can channel that force, if
