00:12:08.500 --> 00:12:10.690 align:middle line:10%
in accordance with one's will.

00:12:10.690 --> 00:12:13.090 align:middle line:84%
By visualizing that
future moment, putting

00:12:13.090 --> 00:12:14.830 align:middle line:84%
in a set of
instructions, and then

00:12:14.830 --> 00:12:17.230 align:middle line:84%
when I let go, turn my
attention away from it,

00:12:17.230 --> 00:12:20.650 align:middle line:84%
my unconscious mind will be
drawn towards experiencing it,

00:12:20.650 --> 00:12:22.960 align:middle line:90%
effortlessly, easily.

00:12:22.960 --> 00:12:25.180 align:middle line:84%
It will seem like the
right thing to do.

00:12:25.180 --> 00:12:28.390 align:middle line:84%
It will seem as though
I'm compelled to do that.

00:12:28.390 --> 00:12:31.330 align:middle line:84%
It'll be automatically
arising from the way

00:12:31.330 --> 00:12:34.720 align:middle line:84%
I've made sense of that
reality moving forward.

00:12:34.720 --> 00:12:37.240 align:middle line:84%
There are a lot of
different ways to do this.

00:12:37.240 --> 00:12:38.650 align:middle line:90%
Is it really magic?

00:12:38.650 --> 00:12:42.990 align:middle line:84%
Depends on how you
define magic, doesn't it?

00:12:42.990 --> 00:12:44.280 align:middle line:90%
>> My name is Dean Radin.

00:12:44.280 --> 00:12:47.540 align:middle line:84%
I'm the chief scientist at the
Institute of Noetic Sciences.

00:12:47.540 --> 00:12:49.920 align:middle line:84%
One of the things that
we do at this institute

00:12:49.920 --> 00:12:55.620 align:middle line:84%
is study experiences that
people report very commonly that

00:12:55.620 --> 00:12:58.800 align:middle line:84%
challenge the prevailing
scientific idea about who

00:12:58.800 --> 00:13:00.960 align:middle line:90%
and what we are.

00:13:00.960 --> 00:13:04.320 align:middle line:84%
And so these experiences
range from simple intuition,

00:13:04.320 --> 00:13:07.680 align:middle line:84%
like gut feelings,
to psychic phenomena,

00:13:07.680 --> 00:13:09.540 align:middle line:90%
to mystical experience.

00:13:09.540 --> 00:13:11.790 align:middle line:84%
We're interested,
then, in when somebody

00:13:11.790 --> 00:13:14.340 align:middle line:84%
has a transformative
experience of this type,

00:13:14.340 --> 00:13:16.910 align:middle line:84%
and there's a pretty
large range of them.

00:13:16.910 --> 00:13:20.010 align:middle line:84%
And we also gain some
sense that the experiences

00:13:20.010 --> 00:13:23.640 align:middle line:84%
that they have are real and
not just an illusion, then

00:13:23.640 --> 00:13:25.800 align:middle line:84%
how do we begin to
understand them?

00:13:25.800 --> 00:13:28.260 align:middle line:84%
Most of what we do in
the scientific sense

00:13:28.260 --> 00:13:29.580 align:middle line:90%
is in the laboratory.

00:13:29.580 --> 00:13:34.930 align:middle line:84%
We use methods like high-density
EEG to look at brain activity.

00:13:34.930 --> 00:13:36.570 align:middle line:84%
We use psychophysiological
methods

00:13:36.570 --> 00:13:40.790 align:middle line:84%
to look at how the brain and
body are related to each other.

00:13:40.790 --> 00:13:43.980 align:middle line:84%
We use methods in physics,
methods in computer science

00:13:43.980 --> 00:13:46.280 align:middle line:90%
and statistics.

00:13:46.280 --> 00:13:48.480 align:middle line:84%
So the magic I'm talking
about, first of all,

00:13:48.480 --> 00:13:51.510 align:middle line:84%
is not Harry Potter, and
it's not Harry Houdini.

00:13:51.510 --> 00:13:52.890 align:middle line:90%
Those are both fictional magic.

00:13:52.890 --> 00:13:54.730 align:middle line:84%
I'm talking about
the real stuff.

00:13:54.730 --> 00:13:58.870 align:middle line:84%
So real magic consists
of three categories.

00:13:58.870 --> 00:14:01.770 align:middle line:84%
The first category we
can call divination.

00:14:01.770 --> 00:14:03.810 align:middle line:84%
It's the idea that
your mind can perceive

00:14:03.810 --> 00:14:05.340 align:middle line:90%
through space and time.

00:14:05.340 --> 00:14:07.520 align:middle line:84%
From a materialistic
point of view,

00:14:07.520 --> 00:14:09.540 align:middle line:84%
we don't know how that
can happen very easily.

00:14:09.540 --> 00:14:12.310 align:middle line:84%
From an idealistic point
of view, it has to happen.

00:14:12.310 --> 00:14:14.220 align:middle line:90%
It is the way things are.

00:14:14.220 --> 00:14:16.860 align:middle line:84%
The second category
I call force of will,

00:14:16.860 --> 00:14:19.350 align:middle line:84%
which from a
scientific perspective,

00:14:19.350 --> 00:14:21.930 align:middle line:84%
we might use terms like
mind-matter interaction

00:14:21.930 --> 00:14:23.982 align:middle line:90%
or psychokinetic effects.

00:14:23.982 --> 00:14:26.190 align:middle line:84%
And that's the notion that
your intention, your will,

00:14:26.190 --> 00:14:27.020 align:middle line:90%
can manifest.

00:14:27.020 --> 00:14:29.310 align:middle line:90%
It makes things happen.

00:14:29.310 --> 00:14:31.470 align:middle line:90%
The third category is theurgy.

00:14:31.470 --> 00:14:35.880 align:middle line:84%
In practice, it's about evoking
spirits in ceremonial magic

00:14:35.880 --> 00:14:39.430 align:middle line:84%
where you try to get spirits
to do things on your behalf.

00:14:39.430 --> 00:14:41.700 align:middle line:84%
So the reason I got
interested in magic

00:14:41.700 --> 00:14:43.350 align:middle line:84%
is because for
most of my career,

00:14:43.350 --> 00:14:46.260 align:middle line:84%
I've been studying
parapsychological phenomena,

00:14:46.260 --> 00:14:48.510 align:middle line:84%
telepathy and
clairvoyance and so on,

00:14:48.510 --> 00:14:51.090 align:middle line:84%
and after studying the
esoteric literature even just

00:14:51.090 --> 00:14:54.480 align:middle line:84%
for a little bit, I realized
that what we had been studying

00:14:54.480 --> 00:14:57.300 align:middle line:84%
in the laboratory is
exactly what people have

00:14:57.300 --> 00:14:59.010 align:middle line:90%
called traditional magic.

00:14:59.010 --> 00:15:02.400 align:middle line:84%
Divination is clairvoyance
and precognition.

00:15:02.400 --> 00:15:04.830 align:middle line:84%
Force of will is
psychokinetic effects.

00:15:04.830 --> 00:15:07.350 align:middle line:84%
Theurgy are phenomena like
near-death experiences

00:15:07.350 --> 00:15:08.670 align:middle line:90%
and medium shift.

00:15:08.670 --> 00:15:13.320 align:middle line:10%
So because I was surprised at
having spent almost 40 years

00:15:13.320 --> 00:15:15.870 align:middle line:10%
studying these phenomena
and not realizing

00:15:15.870 --> 00:15:18.600 align:middle line:10%
that is what traditional
magic is about,

00:15:18.600 --> 00:15:21.720 align:middle line:10%
I decided to write this
book to express essentially

00:15:21.720 --> 00:15:24.030 align:middle line:10%
what I discovered,
which to other people

00:15:24.030 --> 00:15:26.520 align:middle line:10%
might seem, well, of course
it that is the way it is.

00:15:26.520 --> 00:15:28.470 align:middle line:90%
How did you not even know that?

00:15:28.470 --> 00:15:32.180 align:middle line:84%
Part of it is because I went
through the academic tradition,

00:15:32.180 --> 00:15:35.530 align:middle line:84%
where we assume a certain
view of the world.

00:15:35.530 --> 00:15:39.030 align:middle line:84%
And in that view of the world,
ideas of traditional magic

00:15:39.030 --> 00:15:40.500 align:middle line:90%
are laughable.

00:15:40.500 --> 00:15:43.960 align:middle line:90%
It cannot be the case.

00:15:43.960 --> 00:15:48.120 align:middle line:84%
>> My background and interest in
spirituality and science really

00:15:48.120 --> 00:15:49.650 align:middle line:90%
is a lifelong passion.

00:15:49.650 --> 00:15:51.870 align:middle line:84%
Because I started
as a young child

00:15:51.870 --> 00:15:54.630 align:middle line:84%
being very aware of
the fact that there

00:15:54.630 --> 00:15:56.760 align:middle line:84%
is this deeper level
of consciousness

00:15:56.760 --> 00:15:59.580 align:middle line:90%
connecting all of us.

00:15:59.580 --> 00:16:01.950 align:middle line:84%
I wanted to find
out more about that

00:16:01.950 --> 00:16:04.380 align:middle line:90%
and get into the science of it.

00:16:04.380 --> 00:16:06.990 align:middle line:84%
So I chose to go to
UC Berkeley, where

00:16:06.990 --> 00:16:09.540 align:middle line:90%
I got my degree in physics.

00:16:09.540 --> 00:16:13.080 align:middle line:84%
And my main focus of
interest in the program

00:16:13.080 --> 00:16:16.350 align:middle line:84%
had to do with quantum physics,
which I found tremendously

00:16:16.350 --> 00:16:18.960 align:middle line:90%
intuitive for me.

00:16:18.960 --> 00:16:21.480 align:middle line:84%
There has been a lot
of emphasis on the idea

00:16:21.480 --> 00:16:23.430 align:middle line:84%
that magical thinking
doesn't work.

00:16:23.430 --> 00:16:25.890 align:middle line:84%
But actually, it turns
out, magical thinking

00:16:25.890 --> 00:16:27.270 align:middle line:90%
is pretty powerful.

00:16:27.270 --> 00:16:31.150 align:middle line:84%
Because in the quantum realm,
the realm of imagination

00:16:31.150 --> 00:16:31.950 align:middle line:90%
is the king.

00:16:31.950 --> 00:16:34.050 align:middle line:84%
That's the foundation
for everything.

00:16:34.050 --> 00:16:35.445 align:middle line:90%
Consciousness is primary.

