00:16:37.963 --> 00:16:40.380 align:middle line:84%
>> A lot of people who are
attracted to magic in the first

00:16:40.380 --> 00:16:43.890 align:middle line:84%
place, they don't
care how it works.

00:16:43.890 --> 00:16:47.730 align:middle line:84%
They don't even care about the
