00:16:47.730 --> 00:16:49.420 align:middle line:90%
They just want to use it.

00:16:49.420 --> 00:16:50.820 align:middle line:84%
So the two simple
forms that have

00:16:50.820 --> 00:16:53.820 align:middle line:84%
been used as far back as
we can see in history,

00:16:53.820 --> 00:16:55.880 align:middle line:84%
one is called writing
