thing that you want.

00:17:41.860 --> 00:17:43.920 align:middle line:84%
Once you have that
shape, the symbol

00:17:43.920 --> 00:17:46.890 align:middle line:84%
itself will remind
you of the intention.

00:17:46.890 --> 00:17:50.250 align:middle line:84%
You use whatever method
is necessary in order

00:17:50.250 --> 00:17:54.000 align:middle line:84%
to put all of your
intention into that symbol,

00:17:54.000 --> 00:17:57.190 align:middle line:84%
like push through the
symbol to make it happen.

00:17:57.190 --> 00:17:59.940 align:middle line:84%
And then, as is seen in
the laboratory a lot,

00:17:59.940 --> 00:18:02.640 align:middle line:84%
there's something called the
release of effort effect.

00:18:02.640 --> 00:18:05.700 align:middle line:84%
That while you're pushing like
crazy with your intention,

00:18:05.700 --> 00:18:06.990 align:middle line:90%
nothing's going to happen.

00:18:06.990 --> 00:18:09.120 align:middle line:90%
It happens when you release.

00:18:09.120 --> 00:18:10.830 align:middle line:90%
So with the sigil magic as well.

00:18:10.830 --> 00:18:14.100 align:middle line:84%
You push really hard
through this symbol.

00:18:14.100 --> 00:18:15.420 align:middle line:90%
And then you might burn it.

00:18:15.420 --> 00:18:16.920 align:middle line:84%
You might put it
away in a drawer.

00:18:16.920 --> 00:18:19.260 align:middle line:84%
You get rid of it
somehow so that you

00:18:19.260 --> 00:18:23.980 align:middle line:84%
allow the intention to go do
whatever it's going to do.

00:18:23.980 --> 00:18:25.890 align:middle line:84%
>> Some people think
this is something weird.

00:18:25.890 --> 00:18:28.110 align:middle line:84%
And what I'd like
people to realize

00:18:28.110 --> 00:18:31.560 align:middle line:84%
is that basically, every time
we make a choice in our mind,

00:18:31.560 --> 00:18:33.870 align:middle line:84%
we're actually making
a quantum jump.

00:18:33.870 --> 00:18:35.640 align:middle line:84%
Quantum jumping is
such a big field

00:18:35.640 --> 00:18:37.860 align:middle line:84%
that there's a lot
that falls within it.

00:18:37.860 --> 00:18:39.780 align:middle line:84%
Everything from--
the placebo effect

00:18:39.780 --> 00:18:41.880 align:middle line:84%
is, I think, an
excellent example of it,

00:18:41.880 --> 00:18:46.410 align:middle line:84%
to finding lost things, to
suddenly having skill sets

00:18:46.410 --> 00:18:50.880 align:middle line:84%
and abilities where you didn't
have those capabilities before.

00:18:50.880 --> 00:18:53.310 align:middle line:84%
These are all things
that are possible.

00:18:53.310 --> 00:18:54.630 align:middle line:90%
There's really no end in sight.

00:18:54.630 --> 00:18:57.810 align:middle line:84%
Pretty much anything
that you would wish for

00:18:57.810 --> 00:18:59.790 align:middle line:84%
is attainable,
because we're looking

00:18:59.790 --> 00:19:02.760 align:middle line:84%
at the nature of reality
itself and the way that you're

00:19:02.760 --> 00:19:05.260 align:middle line:90%
interacting with it.

00:19:05.260 --> 00:19:06.620 align:middle line:90%
So the steps involved.

00:19:06.620 --> 00:19:09.090 align:middle line:84%
So do you get a
quantum jump from being

00:19:09.090 --> 00:19:12.700 align:middle line:84%
in one state of being, maybe
being sick to being well,

00:19:12.700 --> 00:19:13.500 align:middle line:90%
for example?

00:19:13.500 --> 00:19:15.180 align:middle line:90%
That's a good one.

00:19:15.180 --> 00:19:16.710 align:middle line:84%
The way that you
can make that jump

00:19:16.710 --> 00:19:20.820 align:middle line:84%
is to start by getting into
that relaxed, energized state

00:19:20.820 --> 00:19:22.000 align:middle line:90%
of being.

00:19:22.000 --> 00:19:23.640 align:middle line:84%
So things that are
conducive to that

00:19:23.640 --> 00:19:26.117 align:middle line:84%
would be meditation,
lucid dreaming.

00:19:26.117 --> 00:19:28.450 align:middle line:84%
You can think of that as being
in a theta state of mind.

00:19:28.450 --> 00:19:32.020 align:middle line:84%
It's like a daydream
state of mind.

00:19:32.020 --> 00:19:34.180 align:middle line:84%
And just make that a
regular part of your life.

00:19:34.180 --> 00:19:36.280 align:middle line:84%
So that you feel
like, OK, this is

00:19:36.280 --> 00:19:38.890 align:middle line:84%
how it feels to just
not have any worries.

00:19:38.890 --> 00:19:41.650 align:middle line:90%
You feel energized and relaxed.

00:19:41.650 --> 00:19:43.400 align:middle line:84%
The more you do it,
also, it gets easier.

00:19:43.400 --> 00:19:44.620 align:middle line:90%
So that's good.

