Then the next step
is to really feel

00:19:47.860 --> 00:19:50.500 align:middle line:84%
that you're making a selection
of where you'd like to go.

00:19:50.500 --> 00:19:52.990 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes we don't know
where we want to go.

00:19:52.990 --> 00:19:55.450 align:middle line:84%
I like to then ask,
how good can it get?

00:19:55.450 --> 00:19:57.712 align:middle line:90%
And let that unfold naturally.

00:19:57.712 --> 00:19:59.920 align:middle line:84%
You're talking to your
subconscious when you do that.

00:19:59.920 --> 00:20:02.080 align:middle line:84%
Your subconscious
knows what's good.

00:20:02.080 --> 00:20:04.040 align:middle line:90%
You will go to the right place.

00:20:04.040 --> 00:20:06.350 align:middle line:84%
And so that's a natural
way to guide yourself.

00:20:06.350 --> 00:20:09.260 align:middle line:84%
But if you have a clear
view, I want to get healthy,

00:20:09.260 --> 00:20:10.990 align:middle line:84%
then you can have
that picture in mind.

00:20:10.990 --> 00:20:13.720 align:middle line:84%
To the degree your subconscious
believes that's possible,

00:20:13.720 --> 00:20:16.630 align:middle line:84%
that dictates the degree of
success you're about to have.

00:20:16.630 --> 00:20:18.610 align:middle line:84%
So I recommend,
keep an open mind,

00:20:18.610 --> 00:20:21.010 align:middle line:84%
read lots of
stories and accounts

00:20:21.010 --> 00:20:24.220 align:middle line:84%
of miracles, these magical
happenings, these reality

00:20:24.220 --> 00:20:25.210 align:middle line:90%
shifts.

00:20:25.210 --> 00:20:28.630 align:middle line:84%
Third part is just, act as if
it already happened and you

00:20:28.630 --> 00:20:30.890 align:middle line:90%
behave accordingly.

00:20:30.890 --> 00:20:33.730 align:middle line:84%
And it sounds crazy,
but people experience

00:20:33.730 --> 00:20:37.300 align:middle line:84%
what they're able to experience
based on the energy they bring,

00:20:37.300 --> 00:20:39.490 align:middle line:84%
what their subconscious
really needs.

00:20:39.490 --> 00:20:42.190 align:middle line:84%
Because your subconscious is
in the driver's seat here.

00:20:42.190 --> 00:20:44.170 align:middle line:84%
And what you really
believe and what you need

00:20:44.170 --> 00:20:45.910 align:middle line:84%
is what you're going
to end up getting,

00:20:45.910 --> 00:20:47.250 align:middle line:90%
pretty much all the time.

00:20:47.250 --> 00:20:49.600 align:middle line:84%
When you need it to
happen, it will happen.

00:20:49.600 --> 00:20:52.390 align:middle line:84%
And when you're open minded,
you've brought that energy,

00:20:52.390 --> 00:20:54.295 align:middle line:84%
this is basically the
science of miracles.

00:20:54.295 --> 00:20:57.650 align:middle line:90%


00:20:57.650 --> 00:21:00.980 align:middle line:84%
>> So in the popular sense,
this notion is sometimes thought

00:21:00.980 --> 00:21:03.640 align:middle line:84%
of as, you create
your own reality,

00:21:03.640 --> 00:21:05.870 align:middle line:90%
that your ideas will manifest.

00:21:05.870 --> 00:21:07.460 align:middle line:84%
