extent, positive psychology.

00:21:10.760 --> 00:21:12.620 align:middle line:84%
You can trace that
line of thought

00:21:12.620 --> 00:21:14.360 align:middle line:90%
all the way back to shamanism.

00:21:14.360 --> 00:21:17.075 align:middle line:84%
It is part of the
esoteric tradition.

00:21:17.075 --> 00:21:18.450 align:middle line:84%
So then somebody
could say, well,

00:21:18.450 --> 00:21:21.690 align:middle line:84%
then how come if I want to
have world peace tomorrow,

00:21:21.690 --> 00:21:23.850 align:middle line:84%
I'm thinking about it,
it's not happening.

00:21:23.850 --> 00:21:25.680 align:middle line:90%
So what am I doing wrong?

00:21:25.680 --> 00:21:29.880 align:middle line:84%
Or I want to have a
big, big pile of gold.

00:21:29.880 --> 00:21:33.150 align:middle line:84%
I don't see it, so that
model must be wrong.

00:21:33.150 --> 00:21:36.570 align:middle line:84%
My interpretation of that is
that the conscious level mind

00:21:36.570 --> 00:21:40.290 align:middle line:84%
where this is happening, this
is not where the action happens.

00:21:40.290 --> 00:21:44.220 align:middle line:84%
All of the action happens at
a much deeper level of mind.

00:21:44.220 --> 00:21:46.290 align:middle line:84%
It's a little bit like
looking at an iceberg.

00:21:46.290 --> 00:21:48.540 align:middle line:84%
The tip of the iceberg,
you can see it.

00:21:48.540 --> 00:21:49.990 align:middle line:84%
That's their
conscious awareness.

00:21:49.990 --> 00:21:53.970 align:middle line:84%
But most of it by far
is below the surface.

00:21:53.970 --> 00:21:56.830 align:middle line:84%
And that's where
the action happens.

00:21:56.830 --> 00:22:00.120 align:middle line:84%
>> So it's not just a matter
of telling yourself once a day,

00:22:00.120 --> 00:22:03.900 align:middle line:84%
I can do this, and lots of
people like me succeed at this.

00:22:03.900 --> 00:22:06.840 align:middle line:84%
You're going to need to address
the issues of your heart

00:22:06.840 --> 00:22:10.030 align:middle line:84%
