00:22:14.260 --> 00:22:15.510 align:middle line:90%
A lot of people don't do that.

00:22:15.510 --> 00:22:17.800 align:middle line:84%
They think, I'm just going
to tell myself what to do,

00:22:17.800 --> 00:22:20.140 align:middle line:90%
and it's all going to work.

00:22:20.140 --> 00:22:23.310 align:middle line:84%
>> So one of the reasons why
I wish for a golden Mercedes

00:22:23.310 --> 00:22:26.370 align:middle line:84%
