00:22:30.540 --> 00:22:33.450 align:middle line:84%
We know that we have
self-defeating behaviors,

00:22:33.450 --> 00:22:36.420 align:middle line:84%
otherwise we wouldn't see
levels of obesity that we have

00:22:36.420 --> 00:22:39.510 align:middle line:84%
and people wouldn't drink
and smoke as much as they do.

00:22:39.510 --> 00:22:41.700 align:middle line:84%
So you may consciously
say, I'm not

00:22:41.700 --> 00:22:44.100 align:middle line:84%
going to eat this cookie
because it's not good for me.

00:22:44.100 --> 00:22:46.422 align:middle line:84%
But you will find your hand
going to get the cookie

00:22:46.422 --> 00:22:47.880 align:middle line:84%
and then it will
pick up the cookie

00:22:47.880 --> 00:22:50.208 align:middle line:84%
and it will bring it to your
mouth and you will eat it.

00:22:50.208 --> 00:22:51.625 align:middle line:84%
It's part of your
unconscious that

00:22:51.625 --> 00:22:54.280 align:middle line:84%
can override your
conscious awareness.

00:22:54.280 --> 00:22:57.690 align:middle line:84%
So this is one of the reasons
why meditation as a practice

00:22:57.690 --> 00:23:00.360 align:middle line:84%
is useful, not only for
mental and physical health,

00:23:00.360 --> 00:23:02.490 align:middle line:84%
