00:23:02.490 --> 00:23:04.990 align:middle line:90%
like magical practice.

00:23:04.990 --> 00:23:08.790 align:middle line:10%
In the magical traditions,
what a yogi might call samadhi,

00:23:08.790 --> 00:23:11.850 align:middle line:10%
which is the very deep
levels of mystical unity,

00:23:11.850 --> 00:23:13.775 align:middle line:10%
a magician will call gnosis.

00:23:13.775 --> 00:23:15.150 align:middle line:84%
And all of the
magical traditions

00:23:15.150 --> 00:23:17.820 align:middle line:84%
say that for magic to
work, you have to do it

00:23:17.820 --> 00:23:19.791 align:middle line:90%
from the level of gnosis.

00:23:19.791 --> 00:23:23.020 align:middle line:84%
Well, most people
don't go there.

00:23:23.020 --> 00:23:26.490 align:middle line:84%
It's not easy to get there
