00:26:04.060 --> 00:26:05.080 align:middle line:90%
the doubts and fears.

00:26:05.080 --> 00:26:07.150 align:middle line:90%
You can deal with those.

00:26:07.150 --> 00:26:09.340 align:middle line:84%
The only real
