00:27:18.820 --> 00:27:23.350 align:middle line:84%
And it's so quiet and
so light and so soft.

00:27:23.350 --> 00:27:26.290 align:middle line:84%
Many people miss it
because of all of the noise

00:27:26.290 --> 00:27:29.810 align:middle line:84%
that they've created
in their life.

00:27:29.810 --> 00:27:33.100 align:middle line:84%
>> So the main thing I recommend
